info.description:
# PaReqs

Tool to decode 3DS PaReq and PaRes in Python classes or dict

### Why

I want to try to make a Rust extension module in python for decoding

_**UPD**: inflation (decompression) in Rust lasts 20 times longer ðŸ¤¡_
